        <title>#1616: Catch exceptions when rebuilding the search index</title>
        <pubDate>Fri, 06 Jan 2012 10:11:09 GMT</pubDate>
        
        <dc:creator>amercader</dc:creator>

        <description>&lt;p&gt;
